        <trans-unit id="104" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>This task walks you through running the recognition test and calculating the impairment amount on individual assets.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="105" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Before you can complete this task, you must maintain impairment indicators on individual assets.</source>
